<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Gerando PDF – TalentX</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #1f2937;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .progress {
      height: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .instagram-box {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>⏳ Estamos finalizando seu currículo!</h1>
  <p>Aguarde alguns segundos. Seu PDF está sendo preparado.</p>

 <div class="progress w-75 mx-auto">
  <div id="progressBar" class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-primary"
       role="progressbar" style="width: 0%">0%</div>
</div>
  <div class="instagram-box">
  <h5>Acompanhe mais oportunidades e dicas no nosso Instagram!</h5>
  <p>Siga o <strong>@talentx</strong> e tenha acesso a vagas quentinhas!</p>
  <a href="https://www.instagram.com/talentx" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary mt-2">
    Seguir @talentx no Instagram
  </a>
</div>

<div class="mt-4">
  <p><strong>Veja uma das nossas dicas mais recentes:</strong></p>
  <iframe
    src="https://www.instagram.com/p/DJxtLkXslcO/embed"
    width="320"
    height="400"
    frameborder="0"
    scrolling="no"
    allowtransparency="true">
  </iframe>
</div>


  

<script>
  let progress = 0;
  const bar = document.getElementById('progressBar');
  const interval = setInterval(() => {
    progress += 2; // ajusta para 5s (2% a cada 100ms = 5s total)
    bar.style.width = `${progress}%`;
    bar.textContent = `${progress}%`;

    if (progress >= 100) {
      clearInterval(interval);
      window.location.href = "/download-pdf";
    }
  }, 100);
</script>


</body>
</html>
